draw(A--D);
label("$A$",A,S);
label("$B$",B,S);
label("$C$",C,N);
label("$D$",D,S);
draw(rightanglemark(A,D,B,3));
[/asy]
</think>

The answer is $\boxed{\frac{81\sqrt{3}}{4}}$.

